subset of the larger Utilities sector, made up of companies that provide a mix of services, from electricity to natural gas, water, and other energy-related products. Unlike those that specialize in just one, multis offer investors more diversified</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1094552994/image_1094552994.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742219-sempra-stock-positioned-for-the-future-growth-but-wait-for-a-dip", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 07:21:08"}, {"id": "4742218", "title": "ChargePoint: Good Quarter, Improved Prospects (Rating Upgrade)", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1793097171/image_1793097171.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"ChargePoint EV Electric Vehicle Charging station. ChargePoint plug-in stations are in business parking lots or home use.\" data-id=\"1793097171\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1793097171/image_1793097171.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1793097171/image_1793097171.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1793097171/image_1793097171.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1793097171/image_1793097171.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1793097171/image_1793097171.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1793097171/image_1793097171.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1793097171/image_1793097171.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1793097171/image_1793097171.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">jetcityimage</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><strong><em>Note:</em></strong></p> <p><em>I have covered <strong>ChargePoint Holdings, Inc</strong>. or \"ChargePoint\" (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CHPT\" title=\"ChargePoint Holdings, Inc.\">CHPT</a></span>), previously, so investors should view this as an update to my <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4652537-chargepoint-holdings-disastrous-q3-performance-puts-viability-risk-sell\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4652537-chargepoint-holdings-disastrous-q3-performance-puts-viability-risk-sell\" target=\"_blank\">earlier article</a> on the company.</em></p> <p>After the close of Wednesday's session, electric vehicle (\"EV\") charging solutions provider ChargePoint Holdings </p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1793097171/image_1793097171.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742218-chargepoint-holdings-good-quarter-improved-prospects-chpt-stock", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 07:06:53"}, {"id": "4742217", "title": "CrowdStrike: Despite A Slowdown In Q3, Long-Term Growth Prospects Justify Maintaining A Strong Buy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/138711188/image_138711188.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Hispanic woman holding four-leaf clover\" data-id=\"138711188\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1022px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/138711188/image_138711188.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/138711188/image_138711188.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/138711188/image_138711188.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/138711188/image_138711188.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/138711188/image_138711188.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/138711188/image_138711188.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/138711188/image_138711188.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/138711188/image_138711188.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Jacobs Stock Photography Ltd/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>Introduction and investment thesis</strong></h2> <p>CrowdStrike (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CRWD\" title=\"CrowdStrike Holdings, Inc.\">CRWD</a></span>) <a href=\"https://ir.crowdstrike.com/news-releases/news-release-details/crowdstrike-reports-third-quarter-fiscal-year-2025-financial\" rel=\"nofollow\">reported</a> its first full quarter after its global outage back in July, enabling investors to assess the impacts on the company\u2019s fundamentals. For the first sight, numbers</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/138711188/image_138711188.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742217-crowdstrike-stock-despite-slowdown-q3-long-term-growth-prospects-justify-mainitaining-strong-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 07:01:32"}, {"id": "4742216", "title": "American Coastal: Well-Positioned For Continued Profitability", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1791232359/image_1791232359.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Piggy bank in flood\" data-id=\"1791232359\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1791232359/image_1791232359.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1791232359/image_1791232359.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1791232359/image_1791232359.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1791232359/image_1791232359.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1791232359/image_1791232359.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1791232359/image_1791232359.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1791232359/image_1791232359.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1791232359/image_1791232359.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Thesis Recap</h2> <p>I first <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4704477-american-coastal-insurance-a-remarkable-comeback\">covered</a> American Coastal (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ACIC\" title=\"American Coastal Insurance Corporation\">ACIC</a></span>) in July 2024 with the thesis that it was a contrarian underwriter focused on pricing highly perceived risks carefully to earn exceptional returns on equity. Since my last</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1791232359/image_1791232359.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742216-american-coastal-stock-well-positioned-for-continued-profitability", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 06:50:39"}, {"id": "4742214", "title": "NZF: A High Yielding, Well Run CEF, But The Distribution Is Likely Not Sustainable", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/689019164/image_689019164.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Document with title municipal bond on a table.\" data-id=\"689019164\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/689019164/image_689019164.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/689019164/image_689019164.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/689019164/image_689019164.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/689019164/image_689019164.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/689019164/image_689019164.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/689019164/image_689019164.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/689019164/image_689019164.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/689019164/image_689019164.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">designer491</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><span>When evaluating municipal closed-end bond funds, I currently use a 13-factor evaluation framework. The 13 factors can be useful when comparing different Muni CEF bond funds that are available. There are often several similar Muni bond funds offered by the same</span></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/689019164/image_689019164.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742214-nuveen-municipal-credit-income-high-yielding-cef-distribution-likely-not-sustainable", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 06:31:42"}, {"id": "4742220", "title": "Columbia Dividend Income Fund Q3 2024 Commentary", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1365758819/image_1365758819.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Financial and business background for Stacking of money coins. Savings and Accounts, Finance Banking Business Concept Ideas, Investments, Funds, Bonds, Dividends and Interest.\" data-id=\"1365758819\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1365758819/image_1365758819.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1365758819/image_1365758819.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1365758819/image_1365758819.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1365758819/image_1365758819.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1365758819/image_1365758819.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1365758819/image_1365758819.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1365758819/image_1365758819.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_image